		["references"] = <"Roca O, Messika J, Caralt B, GarcÃ­a-de-Acilu M, Sztrymf B, Ricard JD, Masclans JR. Predicting success of high-flow nasal cannula in pneumonia patients with hypoxemic respiratory failure: The utility of the ROX index. J Crit Care. 2016 Oct;35:200-5. doi: 10.1016/j.jcrc.2016.05.022. Epub 2016 May 31. PMID: 27481760.
">
